---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
import { Picture } from '@astrojs/image/components';
---

<section>
	<Picture
		src={import('~/assets/images/hero-image-3.png')}
		class="mx-auto pt-1"
		widths={[400, 768, 1000]}
		sizes="(max-width: 400px) 400px, (max-width: 768px) 768px, 1000px"
		alt="Hero Image"
		aspectRatio={1798 / 1041}
		loading="eager"
		width={1200}
		height={563}
		style="max-width:100%"
	/>
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-0 sm:px-6">
		<div class="py-3 md:pt-5 pt-3">
			<div class="text-left pb-0 md:pb-0 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<h1
					class="text-center text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-5 font-heading relative top-0"
				>
					Hiding Wallet SeedWords Is<br />
					<span class="text-4xl md:text-6xl sm:text-5xl relative top-2 underline">Not A Security Plan</span>
					<span class="sm:whitespace-nowrap"></span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-center text-2xl max-w-[810px] w-[100%] pb-0 block px-2 lg:pt-8">
					<div class="text-xl text-center pb-4">
						Storing software & hardware wallet seedphrases have <span class="bold">two major problems</span>:<br />
					</div>
					<div
						class="text-xl text-center py-2 bg-gray-900 text-white mb-4 xl:max-w-[850px] lg:max-w-[700px] max-w-[680px] mx-auto rounded-lg w-[96%] px-2"
					>
						If not backed up in multiple offline locations, you're vulnerable to <span class="bold">loss</span>.<br
						/>And if it is, you're open to <span class="bold">theft</span>.
					</div>
					<div class="text-lg text-center pt-2">
						<span class="text-xl bold text-orange-500">We solved both these problems</span><br />Our Hardened Cold
						Storage Backup/Recovery System is like no other: simple, secure & <span class="underline">free</span>
					</div>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
